      {"destination": "London", "text": "Harry Potter fans queue at the Platform 9 3/4 photo op inside King's Cross station, complete with a luggage trolley disappearing into the wall, before browsing the wizarding shop next door."},
      {"destination": "London", "text": "The Victorian arcades of the City of London hide film locations and historic pubs; guided walks cover the Square Mile's markets and alleys."},
      {"destination": "Edinburgh", "text": "The colourful curve of Victoria Street in the Old Town is often cited as an inspiration for Diagon Alley, and Greyfriars Kirkyard holds gravestones bearing names familiar to Harry Potter readers."},
      {"destination": "Mumbai", "text": "Film buffs visit Prithvi Theatre in Juhu, the Kapoor family's intimate playhouse, for evening performances and the famous Irish coffee at the adjoining cafe."},
      {"destination": "Goa", "text": "The Latin Quarter of Fontainhas in Panaji preserves Portuguese-era townhouses in ochre and indigo, with azulejo tiles and narrow lanes best explored on foot."}
